\begin_layout Definition*
The KL-divergence of a density 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho$
\end_inset

 with respect to another density 
\begin_inset Formula $\nu$
\end_inset

 is 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\KL(\rho\|v)=\int\rho(x)\log\frac{\rho(x)}{\nu(x)}dx.
\]

\end_inset


